Clerics who take the Renewal domain seek to further growth, nurture growing things, and work for rebirth and renewal.

<b>Domain Special Ability and Bonus Spells</b>
- Blessing of Renewal: If you fall below 0 hit points, you regain a number of hit points equal to 1d8 + your Charisma modifier. This ability functions once per day.

- The cleric gains access to the following spells at the specified spell level: <i>Charm Person (1), Raise Dead (4), Polymorph Self (8)</i>.